repos_data.description: Suite of tools for deploying and training deep learning models using the JVM. Highlights include model import for keras, tensorflow, and onnx/pytorch, a modular and tiny c++ library for running math code and a java based math library on top of the core c++ library. Also includes samediff: a pytorch/tensorflow like library for running deep learn...
Deep Learning API and Server in C++14 support for PyTorch,TensorRT, Dlib, NCNN, Tensorflow, XGBoost and TSNE
